projectData.name: Thesis
projectData.description: Nearest neighbour value function for chemical retrosynthesis. This project aimed around researching a value function derived from split heuristic for partial structural similarity.

projectData.name: Image Similarity Model
projectData.description: This model uses Representation Learning to group similar images in a N dimensional space and classify the images based on their similarity.

projectData.name: AML Project
projectData.description: This project was a replication of the paper 'Weight Uncertainty in Neural Networks' with an extension of application on Graph Neural Networks

projectData.name: Missile Range Predictor
projectData.description: This project estimates the range of a ballistic missile based on its launch parameters. It uses a Gaussian Process to model the range from a missile simulator.
